OL,5, Teachers used swearing and poo emojis  
OL,6, to criticise vulnerable primary school 
OL,7, pupils in a WhatsApp group chat, BBC   
OL,8, Scotland News can reveal.              
OL,10,FThe existence of the chat between staff
OL,11,Fat Aberdeenshire schools was first     
OL,12,Frevealed last year but the affected    
OL,13,Fpupils' parents were not informed.     
OL,15,FThe messages have now been obtained by 
OL,16,Fthe BBC and show derogatory exchanges  
OL,17,Fabout pupils and parents.              
OL,19,FAberdeenshire Council said nobody was  
OL,20,Fput at risk from the messages.         
